title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
